OL,2,MRotundest Robin: Building a Smart Bird
OL,4,MFeeder That Weighs Songbirds
OL,6,CHugh Evans
OL,7,CFri 11:00-11:30
OL,8,CStage B
OL,10,GHow do you answer a question like "Is
OL,11,Gthe particularly round Robin that
OL,12,Gvisits my bird feeder huge or just
OL,13,Gfluffy?". This talk documents my
OL,14,Gattempt to answer this question by
OL,15,Gbuilding a smart bird feeder that
OL,16,Gtracks the weight of visiting birds,
OL,17,Gwhich in combination with a custom
OL,18,Gcomputer vision model and a night
OL,19,Gvision web cam, helped me build a data
OL,20,Gset of all the visitors to my bird
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
